<br>
** Class Fixes **<br>
<br>
- We THINK we've fixed the problem with the Ranger spell lists. We forgot to change the Ranger spell list to match the Druid spell line when we gave Rangers equal mana to priest classes. This problem should now be corrected.<br>
<br>
- Previously equipment labelled WAR should have read RNG instead. So as not to 'cheat' Warriors out of gear they already have, they may continue to use it as before, EXCEPT if thet move it out of it's current slot. The logic is attached to the item SLOT not the item. Yes, this means your next death as a WAR will mean you can no longer use your existing RNG only gear, but you should have ample time to give it away to your Ranger friends and replace it with Ivy Etched armor (or the equivalent).<br>
<br>
- Rangers now recieve a 40% bonus to their existing AC.<br>
<br>
- Rangers now recieve a 30% bonus to their existing ATK.<br>
<br>
- Rangers now will now have the SAME HP as an Ogre War of the same level and stamina (and equipment). We realize some Ogre Warriors may be upset by this, so we have completely removed the 5% racial experience penalty for Ogres to maintain game balance.<br>
</font><P>Bllack Ader - It's Dr00ds like me that have ruined this land!<P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#212141><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uherdervazaelle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>HerderVazaelle</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>4/18/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>12:39:49 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Community Supporter</FONT><BR></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: Patch Message: April 17, 2001</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">April 17th, 9:00 am<br>
