***-----LATE BREAKING NEWS-----***<br>
** Aerodynamic, Lubricated PIGS **<br>
<br>
- PIGS will now be flying our of Bllack Ader's rear end.  We feel in order to balance the Ranger upgrades, swine need a velocital fix.<br>
